args:
The Halidom is abuzz in preparation for its
upcoming Halloween party. The prince and his
allies—along with Althemia and Edward—
decide to build a Sweet Retreat, but it is
soon beset by fiends. The party then must
protect the house and drive the intruders back.
Gimme a treat, or I'll play a trick on you!
Now cease this foolishness and help us\nwith the party preparations.
Owwww. Feels like you whacked me on the\nhead with a ton of bricks. What WAS that?
...And hey, what's that super thick book?
It is a Halloween cookbook filled with\nhundreds of treat recipes.
One cannot have a Halloween celebration\nwithout Halloween-themed edibles, no?
Let's see... ＂Severed Eyeball Gelatin,＂\nperhaps? Oh, or ＂Flesh-of-the-Damned\nCake with Bloody Raspberry Sauce.＂
Those recipes sound rather terrifying.\nAre you truly going to make them?
Well, do they not strike you as a bit\nover-the-top?
Whoooooa! That big ol' pumpkin is rolling\nlike it means it!
O-obviously not! I'm a researcher;\nI came here to study the castle!
Hauling giant produce around is quite\nfar outside my area of expertise.
Sorry, Althemia. I'll take it from here.
Er, I wasn't trying to say I didn't LIKE\ndoing it...
Permit me to move the pumpkin,\nMaster {player_name}.
But of course. I am your butler, after all.
More importantly, have you any thoughts\nas to the centerpiece for the celebration?
Yes. His Highness mentioned he would like\nto come up with a pièce de résistance to\nbuild excitement at the party.
Yet if we don't get it together soon,\nwe'll not have it ready in time.
Perhaps we could construct a house\nout of candy.
It's Halloween, correct? Well, what better\nexample of the season than treats?
We don't just have to hand treats out;\nwe can build a house out of them and\nthen decorate it.
Ooo, that DOES sound like fun.\nWe can call it the Sweet Retreat!
It certainly sounds like fun. Let's do it!
Eee hee hee!\nThis should be plenty of ingredients!
Hmm? Did I just hear something from over\nthere, or am I imagining things?
This way, Silke. Thank you for your help.
Guess it really was my imagination!
The Snack-o'-Lanterns are baked and ready\nto go, {player_name}.
Them puppies look darn good! Lemme just\nreach over and give 'em a taste tes—
Hands off, you scoundrel! These are for the\nSweet Retreat.
C'mon, who's gonna miss just one?\nYou're makin' a whole pile of 'em!
Do not make me stab you, Ranzal.\nYou as well, Luca! Hands off!
...Er, Luca? When did your arms get so\nthick and scaly and... Um...
That is hardly the most important issue\nto be focusing on!
Oh no! They're going for the other treats!
